==English==

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[New]] [[York]] [[City]]'''

# [[New York, New York]], the greatest city in the world.  Consists of the five [[borough]]s: [[Manhattan]], The [[Bronx]], [[Brooklyn]], [[Queens]] and [[Staten Island]].  Situated at the mouth of the [[Hudson River]], in [[New York State]], in the [[United States of America]].
# [[Manhattan]].

===Usage note===
The term ''New York City'' more often refers to the island of Manhattan alone.  The city’s official name is [[New York, New York]].

